    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Augustis te sancte Curin<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied> <lb n="2"/>digna paramus spectat<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied> <lb n="3"/>nam debita solvere vota <supplied reason="lost">decet</supplied> <lb n="4"/>numenque sacratum <lb n="5"/>ecce venit felixque pat<supplied reason="lost">et</supplied> <lb n="6"/>pristina vota feren<supplied reason="lost">tes</supplied> <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">veni</supplied>mus scimus qui fuerint ipse<supplied reason="lost">met</supplied> <lb n="8"/>isdem sei <note>sic</note> voves <expan><abbr>H</abbr><ex>erculi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>urino</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>V</abbr><ex cert="low">ictori</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>si mi somnia exseri<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">t</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Graffito. Y: Z.1: Erwähnung von Augustus statt Sextilis. (B): Guarducci: Z. 2: spectat statt spectat[a]; Z. 3: dedita solvere vota statt debita solvere vota [decet]; Z. 6: vota feren[tes] / [sci]mus; Z. 8: ces vove statt sei voves; Z.9: si mis omnia ex sen[tentia] statt si mi somnia exseri[t?]. (C): Z. 1: Bezug von Augustis auf feriis oder Kalendis, Nonis, Idibus statt auf diebus.</p>
            </div>
